# E-commerce Prompt Research

Research project for analyzing prompt templates across 7 phases of e-commerce development.

## Quick Start

```bash
# Option 1: Run immediately with /loop
/loop Execute RESEARCH_PROMPT.md with 10-minute intervals

# Option 2: Setup Routine (24/7)
# Go to claude.ai/code/routines and use RESEARCH_PROMPT.md
```

## Files
- `STATE.md` - Heartbeat state (persistent context)
- `RESEARCH_PROMPT.md` - Agent instructions
- `README.md` - Full documentation
- `reports/` - Research outputs
